data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the desirable Adams Lake subdivision. Step inside to an open floor plan with upgraded bamboo flooring and wainscotting throughout. The kitchen features an island, stainless steel appliances, and a walk-in pantry. The living room boasts an entertainment center with built-in shelving, cabinetry, and a cozy fireplace. Both bathrooms are outfitted with marble tile flooring, with the primary bath also showcasing beautifully tiled walls. Fenced-in backyard that offers a spacious 12x26 paver patio, ideal for gatherings or tranquil afternoons. Residents of Adams Lake community enjoy amenities such as a community pool, playground, and park, all while being just minutes from popular restaurants, shopping locales, and I-10.
